title: Updated files to reflect latest developments
body:
The files in this repo were out of date. I made two changes:
1. Moved Presentations to a presentations directory
2. Updated to the README to reflect the latest for Hyperledger. Provided pointers to help people get directed.

title: Update repo list for Sawtooth Lake in Hyperledger Readme
body:
The repos have been consolidated into sawtooth-core. Update the
readme.md file to reflect this.

I mentioned that a consolidation has occurred, to avoid confusion
for those used to the old system.

title: I've fixed up your hyperledger with a working blockchain implementation
Description Update for the Elements Project
body:
This pull request updates the description of [the Elements Project](https://elementproject.org), adding context to the concept of sidechains and cross-chain interoperability.

For a more in-depth explanation, please [Gregory Maxwell's introduction to the Elements Project and sidechains](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9pyVvq-vrrM).
